reviewText: Love it, such a good movie.
Received it quickly, however, it is defective and won"t play.  I have contacted the seller via email twice and I have not been contacted.

This is a must see for any women who has gone through
or is going through a mastectomy!  My friend understood
all that you go through when you have breast cancer.
This is such an awesome movie, I laughed & cried through the whole thing, you need a box of tissues but really worth watching.!!!!
